#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Selecting document to print at the bottom of the the distributor page</h2>
This select has two options:
<center><table><tr><th>Option</th><th>Use</th></tr>
<tr><th align=left>Staff</th><td>
    This option will put up a page suitable for taking initial information from a
    new driver or staff member.  The page can either be filled out directly (unusual),
    or printed, and copies to hand to people as they appear.  The printed page will have
    a QR code on the top that they can follow to fill out the form themselves.
</td></tr>
<tr><th align=left>Patron</th><td>
    This option will put up a page suitable for taking initial information from a
    new patron.  The page can either be filled out directly (unusual),
    or printed, with copies to hand to patrons as they are interviewed.  The
    printed page will have a QR code on the top that they can follow to fill out
    the form themselves.
</td></tr>
</table></center>
